column5: Holy fuck! You know your way around that box. Really inspired me to make some glitchier stuff on mine. :)
Yeah that's kinda what I'm trying to say. I agree.

Hey, she is a lot more important to me than smoking weed once a week. That's why I got so upset about what she said. Because it's not how I feel. And if that's what she honestly thinks, then I don't know if she appreciates me for all the time, support and love that I give her.

I think you'll find it's the former "bro". I don't have the time to mention all problems and contributing factors here. I would be writing for a while. Because these things aren't just black and white.
Thanks for that! I just woke up and that's very reasonable advice. I hope your relationship goes well man!
Yes. Speed has high potential for abuse. Be careful and learn to spell.
Happy birthday mate! Fuck depression. Don't let it steal your life xx
